{"tid":915364,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"聯手打造《英雄聯盟》宇宙 Marvel x LOL合推漫畫《LOL: ASHE: WARMOTHER》","createTime":"2018-11-25T02:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T07:10:24.000Z","uid":125998,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63d938346e6a837cc26d0ac4e94b1de66c0db93a","tid":915364,"uid":125998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:35:13.000Z","msg":"全球最著名的線上遊戲《英雄聯盟》將聯同Marvel 合作，首度推出漫畫《LEAGUE OF LEGENDS: ASHE: WARMOTHER》，並由Riot Games的作家Odin Austin Shafer寫劇本，而Nina Vakueva 和 Cardinal Rae則擔全繪圖和插畫。<br />\n<br />\nMarvel的主編C.B. Cebulski指《英雄聯盟》是遊戲業界中最著名的線上遊戲之一，當中的人物和其故事十分適合繪創成為漫畫，是次合作，希望能一同打造出屬於「英雄聯盟的宇宙世界」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRiot Games的創意總監Greg Street則指《英雄聯盟》與《MCU》十分相似，同樣有豐富背景的角色，而是次很高興能與Marvel一同合作，將《英雄聯盟》的故事轉變為現實。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/lol_4864471205bf7ef8ef2b1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Flol_4864471205bf7ef8ef2b1a.jpg&h=18b077d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事內容<br />\n漫畫《LEAGUE OF LEGENDS: ASHE: WARMOTHER》顧名思義是以ASHE擔任主角，故事內容大概是會帶領大家走入《英雄聯盟》的世界觀內的「Freljord」進行冒險之旅，故事主角ASHE是北境寒霜的後裔，有著神奇聯繫的戰士，期間會不斷嘗試揭開神秘又古遠的符文大地，同時亦遇到不同的危機。"},{"pid":"f3755229d9a6541cfd1aea419dca4f1a0a0573f6","tid":915364,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"冰原好似都有排寫<br />\nASHE同老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef49a7f9ce67b90c2e075778811e117cc39f20a5","tid":915364,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3755229d9a6541cfd1aea419dca4f1a0a0573f6","tid":915364,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"冰原好似都有排寫<br />\nASHE同老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T03:27:09.000Z","msg":"豬女、ashe、蠻王三角戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6074a9b7d7261a